Python – install from Download Python | Python.org
Click on add to Path

Use Pip to install Pandas, Matplotlib and Seaborn
  For ex: pip install pandas
  
For Geopandas, libraries – GDAL & Fiona is required
  Install GDAL first and then Fiona.
  Pip direct method doesn’t work
  We will download wheel file and use pip. 
  Website: Archived: https://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/  
  Copy the location of the downloaded wheel package and use pip
    Run a similar code on the command prompt: pip install C:\\Users\\----\\Downloads\\gdal-1.6.0-cp310-cp310-win_amd64.whl

